title: Bug 109350 - Output parameter not displaying in data set dialog
description: The output parameter is not visible in the data set dialog on the query result page.
OB: While in the query result page, there is no data returned. The actual result is that the output parameter does not display in the edit data set dialog.
EB: Expect the output parameter to be visible and displayed in the edit data set dialog on the query result page.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Navigate to the query result page.
2. Perform a query that should have output parameters.
3. Open the edit data set dialog and observe that the output parameter is not displayed.
